@alexToken = course-alex-local-token

### Seed the course customer and the existing ticket T-1001
POST http://localhost:8080/api/demo/seed

### Inspect the exact model-visible action allowlist
GET http://localhost:8080/api/assistant/actions
Authorization: Bearer {{alexToken}}

### Read action: no confirmation and no model-supplied identity
POST http://localhost:8080/api/assistant/orchestrate
Authorization: Bearer {{alexToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What is the status of ticket T-1001?",
  "conversationId": "course-actions-read"
}

### Incomplete write: must clarify and create no pending action or ticket
POST http://localhost:8080/api/assistant/orchestrate
Authorization: Bearer {{alexToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Create a high-priority support ticket titled Account locked.",
  "conversationId": "course-actions-write"
}

### Complete write: must return CONFIRMATION_REQUIRED without mutation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/assistant/orchestrate
Authorization: Bearer {{alexToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Create a high-priority ticket titled Account locked and explain that recovery emails never arrive.",
  "conversationId": "course-actions-write"
}

### Confirm in the same owner and conversation: executes exactly once
POST http://localhost:8080/api/assistant/orchestrate
Authorization: Bearer {{alexToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "yes",
  "conversationId": "course-actions-write"
}

### Duplicate confirmation: must report that no pending action remains
POST http://localhost:8080/api/assistant/orchestrate
Authorization: Bearer {{alexToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "yes",
  "conversationId": "course-actions-write"
}
